<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٣٩٦]</span> الحَارِثُ بْنُ ثُوَبَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> الأَسَدِيُّ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَأَى عَلِيًّا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>رَوَى عَنْهُ عَبَّاسُ بنُ ذَرِيحٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>يُعَدُّ في الكُوفيينَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٢٣٩٧]</span> الحَارِثُ بْنُ ثَقْفٍ <span class="c2">(٤)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عَنِ الحَسَنِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>رَوَى عَنْهُ يحيى بنُ اليَمَانِ <span class="c2">(٦)</span>، ومُحمدُ بنُ يُوسفَ، قَوْلَهُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
